WEBVTT

00:00:01.375 --> 00:00:05.000
This is an elementary school
in Columbus, Ohio.

00:00:05.875 --> 00:00:09.292
And inside of this school
there was a student named D.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:12.809
When D started school here
he was six years old:

00:00:12.833 --> 00:00:14.101
cute as a button,

00:00:14.125 --> 00:00:16.332
with a smile that brightened
the entire room.

00:00:17.667 --> 00:00:19.893
But after a few months in school,

00:00:19.917 --> 00:00:21.768
D became angry,

00:00:21.792 --> 00:00:23.167
and that smile faded.

00:00:24.750 --> 00:00:28.226
D began to do things like flip tables,

00:00:28.250 --> 00:00:30.059
throw desks and chairs,